Name: Fantasy Jigsaw Puzzle
About the game: Challenging 6 x 6 jigsaw puzzle featuring fantasy female characters. Relaxing background music to match the fantasy theme. The game features 12 puzzles which you can solve in any order of your choice. There is no time limit, but there is a timer in case you want to see how quickly you can solve each puzzle. Be among the fastest puzzle solvers to achieve a top spot in our Leaderboards and unlock various achievements.
